---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Profile | Astore 1 GBA 13</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&family=Syne:wght@800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,600&family=Archivo+Black&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --flag-red: #cc0000;
        --flag-black: #000000;
        --flag-green: #006600;
        --d-gold: #BA8E23;
        --hud-bg: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.95);
      }
      
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      body { 
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
        background-color: #050505; 
        color: white; 
        margin: 0; 
        padding-top: 100px; 
        overflow-x: hidden; 
      }

      /* SYNCED COMMAND HUD */
      .command-hud {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 70px;
        background: var(--hud-bg); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--d-gold);
        display: flex; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center;
        padding: 0 40px; z-index: 1000; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }
      .hud-logo { 
        font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif; color: var(--d-gold); 
        text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 2px;
      }
      .hud-nav { display: flex; gap: 30px; margin-left: 40px; }
      .hud-link { 
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; font-size: 11px; 
        font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; 
      }
      .hud-link:hover, .hud-link.active { color: var(--d-gold); }

      /* DOSSIER LAYOUT */
      .dossier-container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .dossier-header {
        border-left: 8px solid var(--flag-red);
        padding-left: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
      }

      .dossier-header h1 {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
        color: var(--d-gold);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 0.9;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .grid-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
        gap: 50px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }

      /* SIDEBAR SPECS */
      .sidebar {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(186, 142, 35, 0.2);
        border-top: 4px solid var(--flag-green);
      }
      
      .sidebar h3 {
        color: var(--d-gold);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        padding-bottom: 5px;
      }
      
      .sidebar p { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.5; }

      /* MAIN CONTENT */
      .main-content p {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #eee;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .highlight-text { color: var(--d-gold); font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <header class="command-hud">
      <a href="/" class="hud-logo">G-B ELECTIONS 2026</a>
      <nav class="hud-nav">
        <a href="/" class="hud-link">Home</a>
        <a href="/profile" class="hud-link active">Candidate Profile</a>
        <a href="/promises" class="hud-link">Campaign Promises</a>
        <a href="/jobs" class="hud-link">Jobs Portal</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="dossier-container">
      <div class="dossier-header">
        <span style="letter-spacing: 5px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 12px; color: var(--flag-red);">OFFICIAL DOSSIER</span>
        <h1>Major (R) <br/> Fahad Hanif Khan</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-layout">
        <div class="sidebar">
          <h3>Service Record</h3>
          <p>Ex-Military Officer (Retired). Decades of disciplined leadership, strategic planning, and operational execution under pressure.</p>
          
          <h3>Core Competency</h3>
          <p>Administrative governance, technological integration, and rapid infrastructure deployment.</p>
          
          <h3>Jurisdiction</h3>
          <p>A native son of Astore, GBA-13, bringing a global technological perspective to local challenges.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="main-content">
          <p>Major (R) Fahad Hanif Khan stands at the intersection of traditional discipline and futuristic progress. Having served with distinction, he brings a military-grade approach to the administrative and economic challenges facing GBA-13.</p>
          
          <p>His vision is unwavering: to elevate Astore from a geographically isolated region into a <span class="highlight-text">digital gateway</span>. He understands that the future economy is borderless, and physical isolation should no longer mean economic isolation.</p>

          <p>By bridging the education gap with high-level technical certifications and remote-work infrastructure, he aims to secure the economic sovereignty of every household in the constituency. Integrity is the foundation. Action is the language. Results are the only metric.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>